  description: "decimal.InvalidOperation __flags__, __basicsize__, __itemsize__ type checks and cross-class consistency — wave 538 theme: decimal.InvalidOperation is a pure-Python subclass of decimal.DecimalException; all three C-slot attributes are integer-typed; cross-checks with Decimal and Context to confirm consistency across C and Python decimal types; verified with Python 3.12"
